item_powerup_ranged_accuracy_01_01	Tactical Scope	This powerup will increase the accuracy of your weapon, but will also decrease the rate at which it can fire.  In addition, all powered up weapons decay at an increased rate.  Each shot fired has a chance to decrease the weapon's condition.	object/tangible/powerup/weapon/ranged_accuracy.iff							2		powerup.pup		1	
item_powerup_ranged_eledamage_01_01	Tuning Coupler	This powerup can only be applied to weapons with elemental damage.   This powerup will increase the amount of elemental damage a ranged weapon will do, but will also decrease the amount of normal damage done.  In addition, all powered up weapons decay at an increased rate.  Each shot fired has a chance to decrease the weapon's condition.	object/tangible/powerup/weapon/ranged_eledamage.iff							2		powerup.pup		1	
item_powerup_ranged_damage_01_01	High Power Barrel	This powerup will increase the damage output of a ranged weapon, but will also decrease the speed at which you can fire it.  In addition, all powered up weapons decay at an increased rate.  Each shot fired has a chance to decrease the weapon's condition.	object/tangible/powerup/weapon/ranged_damage.iff							2		powerup.pup		1	
item_powerup_melee_eledamage_01_01	Element Dispersal Tuning Kit	This powerup can only be applied to weapons with elemental damage.   This powerup will increase the amount of elemental damage a melee will do, but will also decrease the amount of normal damage done.  In addition, all powered up weapons decay at an increased rate.  Each hit has a chance to decrease the weapon's condition.	object/tangible/powerup/weapon/melee_eledamage.iff							2		powerup.pup		1	
item_powerup_melee_actioncost_01_01	Hilt Reinforcement Kit	This powerup will decrease the action cost of specials, but will also decrease the accuracy of the weapon.  In addition, all powered up weapons decay at an increased rate.  Each hit has a chance to decrease the weapon's condition.	object/tangible/powerup/weapon/melee_actioncost.iff							2		powerup.pup		1	
item_powerup_melee_damage_01_01	Inertial Fluctuator Kit	This powerup will increase the damage output of a melee weapon, but will also decrease the speed at which you can swing it.  In addition, all powered up weapons decay at an increased rate.  Each hit has a chance to decrease the weapon's condition.	object/tangible/powerup/weapon/melee_damage.iff							2		powerup.pup		1	
item_powerup_melee_wound_01_01	Surface Serration Kit	This powerup will increase the wounds your weapon will generate, but will also increase the action cost for specials.  In addition, all powered up weapons decay at an increased rate.  Each hit has a chance to decrease the weapon's condition.	object/tangible/powerup/weapon/melee_wound.iff							2		powerup.pup		1	
item_powerup_melee_speed_01_01	Tactical Grip Kit	This powerup will increase the rate at which you can attack with this weapon, but will also decrease the accuracy of your attacks.  In addition, all powered up weapons decay at an increased rate.  Each hit has a chance to decrease the weapon's condition.	object/tangible/powerup/weapon/melee_speed.iff							2		powerup.pup		1	
item_powerup_melee_accuracy_01_01	Weight Balancing Kit	This powerup will increase the accuracy of your weapon, but will also decrease the rate at which you can swing it.  In addition, all powered up weapons decay at an increased rate.  Each hit has a chance to decrease the weapon's condition.	object/tangible/powerup/weapon/melee_accuracy.iff							2		powerup.pup		1	
item_roadmap_spice_booster_blue_01_02	Booster Blue	An out-of-use industrial dye employed in starship manufacturing that when consumed, enhances the user's physical reaction time.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_booster_blue_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_crash_n_burn_01_02	Crash 'n Burn	A rare chemical mix of stimulant and depressive, Crash n' Burn heightens the user's awareness while at the same time increasing latent psychodepressive tendencies.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_crash_n_burn_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_droid_lube_01_02	Droid Lube	Zypolene Droid Lubricant was once used as a very common homemade joint and servo lubricant for robot servants.  After medical studies suggested the substance was the cause of cellular decay among various races, the use of zypolene decreased.  It has a burning, stimulating effect when rubbed across open skin.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_droid_lube_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_giggledust_01_02	Giggledust	An all natural dust that is inhaled to create a sense of euphoria and alertness.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_giggledust_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_grey_gabaki_01_02	Grey Gabaki	A plant named for its drab color when dried, Grey Gabaki gives off a light and relaxing smoke when burned.  It is commonly used in cantinas, but some merchants also burn it to make store fronts a more relaxing environment for customers.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_grey_gabaki_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_gunjack_01_02	Gunjack	A highly concentrated methylpenatox and glucose based chemical cocktail that grants the user intense physical strength while decreasing fine motor control and the ability to reason.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_gunjack_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_kliknik_boost_01_02	Kliknik Boost	An extract from the Kliknik immune system, this chemical coats the users organs with an ultra thin protective layer that insulates them during heavy exertion.  Can cause severe nausea when the body attempts to remove the coating.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_kliknik_boost_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_kwi_boost_01_02	Kwi Boost	A gland which secretes a fluid into the kwi bloodstream which increases their base regeneration in response to an attack.  Can cause burnout after the boost has run its course.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_kwi_boost_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_muon_gold_01_02	Muon Gold	A subatomic reactant that results in intense mental clarity and focus.  Banned by Imperial authorities due to its degenerative effect on neural pathways.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_muon_gold_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_neutron_pixey_01_02	Neutron Pixey	A calming hallucinogen of unknown alien origin, Neutron Pixie is usually ingested with a light fruit flavoring to increase palatability.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_neutron_pixey_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_pyrepenol_01_02	Pyrepenol	A concentrated pyrepenol pill.  When consumed it results in heightened physical strength.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_pyrepenol_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_scramjet_01_02	Scramjet	"""Scramjet"" is the rough street name for a body building food additive.  Due to its distorting and potentially harmful effects on humanoid biology, scramjet has been outlawed on Imperial worlds."	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_scramjet_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_sedative_h4b_01_02	H4B Sedative	A medical sedative used on battle fields to treat traumatic injuries.  H4b's strong depressive properties result in it often being used for recreational purposes.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_sedative_h4b_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_shadowpaw_01_02	Shadowpaw	Shadowpaw is the name of the powder that remains when the Edorian Itassi root is ground up.  This powder was originally used by the native Ewok race in spiritual ceremonies via a long bone pipe, but has since found a place in various cantinas and criminal dives.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_shadowpaw_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_sweetblossom_01_02	Sweetblossom	A thick fluid made from the Sweetblossom with strong sedative properties.  Sometimes used as a field anesthetic or truth serum.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_sweetblossom_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_thruster_head_01_02	Thruster Head	Thruster Head is the street name for an intense synaptic enhancement stim.  When injected Thruster Head multiplies the user's mental capabilities ten fold, at the cost of increased anxiety and extreme nausea.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_thruster_head_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_spice_yarrock_01_02	Yarrock	A root derived spice with strong mind enhancing properties.	object/tangible/loot/npc_loot/spice_yarrock_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,item.spice		1	
item_roadmap_deed_speederbike_01_02	Speederbike Deed	Using this deed will create a new vehicle in your datapad.	object/tangible/loot/generic_deed/vehicle_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,systems.vehicle_system.vehicle_deed		1	
item_roadmap_deed_speederbike_swoop_01_02	Swoop Deed	Using this deed will create a new vehicle in your datapad.	object/tangible/loot/generic_deed/vehicle_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,systems.vehicle_system.vehicle_deed		1	
item_roadmap_deed_landspeeder_x31_01_02	X-31 Landspeeder Deed	Using this deed will create a new vehicle in your datapad.	object/tangible/loot/generic_deed/vehicle_generic.iff							2		item.special.nomove,systems.vehicle_system.vehicle_deed		1	
weapon_grenade_fragmentation_01_01	Fragmentation Grenade	"The C12 Fragmentation Grenade is a variant of hand-thrown explosive charge which fills its immediate area with high-speed projectiles upon detonation. To throw the grenade, click on it in your inventory and choose ""throw"".  Alternately, drag it into your toolbar, then use the corresponding toolbar key during combat to throw it. Grenades usually come in a stack."	object/weapon/ranged/grenade/grenade_fragmentation_generic.iff	weapon		1			3	2		systems.combat.combat_weapon,systems.combat.combat_grenade		1	
item_pet_egg_chuba_01_01	Chuba DNA	This is high quality DNA of a chuba. It can be used in a Beast Master's incubator to create a Chuba pet.	object/tangible/loot/beast/dna_container.iff							2		systems.beast.dna	3	1	
item_pet_mount_carrion_01_01	Kartha's Cliff-Jumper	A mount given to you for your efforts in assisting Kartha.	object/tangible/deed/pet_deed/carrion_spat_generic_deed.iff							2		item.special.nomove,npc.pet_deed.reward_pet_deed		1	
item_npe_health_buff_01_01	Anabolic Compounds	When used this item will increase your constitution for a time.	object/tangible/medicine/instant_stimpack/stimpack_generic_e_st_3.iff						4	2	50	item.buff_click_item		1	
item_npe_stamina_buff_01_01	Mark I Adrenal Stimulator	Electrically stimulates your own body's production of adrenaline without the use of chemicals. When used this item will increase your stamina for an amount of time.	object/tangible/loot/generic_usable/worklight_generic.iff						4	2	50	item.buff_click_item		1	
item_npe_will_buff_01_01	Bookchip: Poetry and Musings	A compilation by various authors from all over the galaxy containing a wide collection of poetry and short stories. Great for a quick and inspiring read! When used this item will increase your agility for a period of time.	object/tangible/loot/generic_usable/handheld_viewscreen_2_generic.iff						3	2	50	item.buff_click_item		1	
item_npe_rng_speed_buff_01_01	Trigger Lubrication Silicate	Helps to prevent sticking and jamming on mechanical weapon parts. When used this item will increase your precision for a period of time.	object/tangible/loot/generic_usable/large_dispersal_unit_generic.iff						3	2	50	item.buff_click_item		1	
item_npe_melee_speed_buff_01_01	Aero-Coat Weapon Spray	This spray helps to reduce wind resistance. Particularly useful when you're swinging something at someone. When used this item will increase your strength.	object/tangible/loot/generic/battery_useable_generic.iff						3	2	50	item.buff_click_item		1	
item_npe_backpack_reward_01_01	Simple Outdoorsman Pack	Designed for those who love to travel. If worn on your back, you can store up to 50 more items within it. Backpacks are also useful for organizing inventory items and for increasing the number of items you can carry.	object/tangible/wearables/backpack/backpack_s01.iff							2	350	item.special.nomove		1	
