item_krayt_pearl_04_01	Krayt Dragon Pearl	A gizzard stone used by the Krayt Dragon to help it digest its food. The stone is a lustrous, milky color and can be tuned by a Jedi for use as a focusing crystal in a lightsaber.||This pearl must be tuned by a Jedi before use.  Once tuned this pearl becomes a part of the lightsaber's focusing device and can only be used in a lightsaber by the Jedi who tuned it.	object/tangible/component/weapon/lightsaber/lightsaber_module_krayt_dragon_pearl.iff							4		systems.jedi.jedi_saber_component		1	
