col_dooku_datadisk_02_01	Dooku's Story - Data disk 1	Padawan - The data disk tells the story of Dooku's youth and training in the Jedi Order. Born from nobility, the young Dooku was trained as a jedi from an early age. During his years as a padawan he trained under some of the greatest jedi of his time, including Jedi Master Yoda.	object/tangible/loot/creature_loot/collections/dooku_datadisk_01.iff							1	1000	systems.collections.consume_loot,object.autostack		1	Story of Count Dooku
col_dooku_datadisk_02_02	Dooku's Story - Data disk 2	Jedi Master - The data disk describes Dooku's promotion to Jedi Knight and the training of padawans of his own, including Qui-Gon Jinn. Dooku was granted the rank of Jedi Master with Qui-Gon Jinn's successful passage from Padawan to Jedi Knight.	object/tangible/loot/creature_loot/collections/dooku_datadisk_02.iff							1	1000	systems.collections.consume_loot,object.autostack		1	Story of Count Dooku
col_dooku_datadisk_02_03	Dooku's Story - Data disk 3	Leaving the Order - The data disk tells of Dooku and his loss of faith in the Republic and the Jedi Order. Shortly after the Battle of Naboo and the death of his former student, Qui-Gon Jinn, Dooku formally left the Jedi Order.	object/tangible/loot/creature_loot/collections/dooku_datadisk_03.iff							1	1000	systems.collections.consume_loot,object.autostack		1	Story of Count Dooku
col_dooku_datadisk_02_04	Dooku's Story - Data disk 4	Embracing the Dark Side - The data disk contains the story of how Dooku assumed his inherited title of Count and rose to be one of the leaders of the Separatists' Movement prior to the outbreak of the Clone War.	object/tangible/loot/creature_loot/collections/dooku_datadisk_04.iff							1	1000	systems.collections.consume_loot,object.autostack		1	Story of Count Dooku
col_dooku_datadisk_02_05	Dooku's Story - Data disk 5	Dooku's Death - On the final data disk, the last years of Count Dooku's life are recorded. Here, many of his actions during the Clone War are told. The story ends with his death, at the hands of Anakin Skywalker, during the Battle of Coruscant.	object/tangible/loot/creature_loot/collections/dooku_datadisk_05.iff							1	1000	systems.collections.consume_loot,object.autostack		1	Story of Count Dooku
