item_jedi_robe_06_03	Shatterpoint Cloak	A complex Force phenomenon called a Shatterpoint denotes a weakness or flaw that if taken advantage of could cause even the most insurmountable to crumble. A single 'strike', or action, could cause events to transpire completely differently than they might otherwise have done. Often, they existed for only brief moments, as shatterpoints could be affected by actions as small as movement. The ability to perceive shatterpoints was very rare and the only being known to have perceived them with comparative ease was Mace Windu.	object/tangible/wearables/robe/robe_s33_h1.iff			90	force_sensitive			6		item.special.nomove,item.buff_worn_item,item.set_bonus_item,systems.jedi.jedi_cloak		1	
item_jedi_robe_06_04	Cloak of Hate	"""Some possess raw elemental power; they can unleash storms of lightning from their fingertips?"""	object/tangible/wearables/robe/robe_s32_h1.iff			90	force_sensitive			6		item.special.nomove,item.buff_worn_item,item.set_bonus_item,systems.jedi.jedi_cloak		1	
item_jedi_robe_06_05	Shatterpoint Cloak	A complex Force phenomenon called a Shatterpoint denotes a weakness or flaw that if taken advantage of could cause even the most insurmountable to crumble. A single 'strike', or action, could cause events to transpire completely differently than they might otherwise have done. Often, they existed for only brief moments, as shatterpoints could be affected by actions as small as movement. The ability to perceive shatterpoints was very rare and the only being known to have perceived them with comparative ease was Mace Windu.	object/tangible/wearables/robe/robe_s33.iff			90	force_sensitive			6		item.special.nomove,item.buff_worn_item,item.set_bonus_item,systems.jedi.jedi_cloak		1	
