publish_gift_chapter_11_snow_machine_02_01	Hoth Snow Machine	While in your inventory, you can use this snow-maker to create snowballs to throw at others.||While placed in your house, this machine can be turned on to give the illusion of snow falling in the room of your choice.	object/tangible/item/publish_gift_chapter_11_snow_machine.iff							1		item.publish_gift.snow_machine,item.special.nomove			
