item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_general_grievous_gutsack	General Grievous' Gutsack	A pressurized cyborg gutsack whose nutrient-rich fluids are capable of enhancing a person's learning capabilities when ingested.  Draining and drinking from the gutsack will provide a 20% increase on experience points earned within the one hour duration.  If you are level 90, this loot will grant you one random collection item.  This item is consumable.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/consumable_general_grievous_gutsack.iff						1	4		item.special.nomove,item.buff_click_item,object.autostack			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_hh_15_torpedo_warhead	HH-15 Torpedo Warhead	This missile is favored among the Rebel Alliance vanguard units for use in the Golan Arms HH-15 projectile launcher.  This buff provides the user a 10% increase on all Galactic Civil War (GCW) points earned in one hour.  This item is consumable.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/consumable_hh_15_torpedo_warhead.iff						1	4		item.special.nomove,item.buff_click_item,object.autostack			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_wookiee_ceremonial_pipe	Wookiee Ceremonial Pipe	This ornate hand-crafted pipe is used in several important ceremonies in Wookiee culture.  When used, this item will grant you one random collection item.  This item is consumable.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/consumable_wookiee_ceremonial_pipe.iff						1	4		item.special.nomove,item.buff_click_item,object.autostack			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_jango_fett_memorial_statue	Jango Fett Memorial Statue	This life-sized statue is a memorial to one of the greatest bounty hunters of all time.  Jango Fett was so proficient at combat that he served as the template for the Republic's clone army.  This item is #1 in a series of four Build-A-Jetpack items.  Combine this item with Build-A-Jetpack items 2, 3, and 4 to create a Merr-Sonn JT-12 jetpack.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/combine_object_jango_fett_memorial_statue.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_combine_tcg_items			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_boba_fett_statue	Boba Fett Statue	The most feared bounty hunter in the Galaxy, Boba Fett, is now available for display in your house as a life-sized statue.  Outlaws and criminals will tremble in its presence.  Boba Fett is sure to be a fine centerpiece to any collection.  This item is #2 in a series of four Build-A-Jetpack items.  Combine this item with Build-A-Jetpack items 1, 3, and 4 to create a Merr-Sonn JT-12 jetpack.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/combine_object_boba_fett_statue.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_combine_tcg_items			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_emperor_palpatine_statuette	Emperor Palpatine Statuette	A meter-high statue of the most powerful figure in the Galaxy.  Once an unassuming Senator from the sovereign system of Naboo, Palpatine was elected Supreme Chancellor after a Vote of No Confidence in Chancellor Valorum's leadership.  During his term as Chancellor, Palpatine lead the Old Republic to a victory in the Clone Wars.  This victory, along with the defeat of the mutinous Jedi, allowed him the power and influence to declare himself Emperor and institute the New Order.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/decorative_emperor_palpatine_statuette.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_sith_meditation_room_deed	Structure Deed: Sith Meditation Room	An intimidating spire that serves as a lightning rod to help loyal Sith tap into the very essence of the dark side of the Force.  This black structure stands as a monument of doom to all the remaining Jedi in the Galaxy.  This structure consumes two lots and may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/structure_deed_sith_meditation_room_deed.iff							4		item.special.nomove,item.structure_deed.player_structure_deed			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_jedi_meditation_room_deed	Structure Deed: Jedi Meditation Room	A beacon of peace and light in these dark times, the Jedi Meditation Room reflects the values and tranquility (as well as the outward appearance) of the Jedi Temple that was once the center of Jedi activity for the entire Galaxy.  From the calming chamber inside, a Jedi may center themselves and focus on enlightenment.  This structure consumes two lots and may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/structure_deed_jedi_meditation_room_deed.iff							4		item.special.nomove,item.structure_deed.player_structure_deed			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_podracer_longtail	Vehicle Deed: IPG-X1131 Longtail Engine Podracer	Perfect for speed lovers, this IPG-X1131 Longtail Engine Podracer similar to the one flown by Teemto Pagalies in the Boonta Eve Classic.  This seemingly un-aerodynamic pod is designed around a gyroscopic stabilizer ring that rotates at 230rpm that gives it excellent stability.  This item may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/vehicle_deed_podracer_longtail.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.vehicle_system.vehicle_deed			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_koro2_exodrive_airspeeder	Vehicle Deed: Koro-2 Exodrive Airspeeder	This sleek airspeeder built by The Desler Gizh Outworld Mobility Corporation is perfect for whipping around the Galaxy in style.  Similar to the airspeeder flown by the late bounty hunter Zam Wesell, the forward mandibles of the Koro-2 intensely irradiate the air around them, inducing ionization and making it conductive. Paired electrodes then electrify the airstream, and it is magnetically propelled toward the rear of the craft, resulting in the air literally dragging the vessel through the sky.  This item may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/vehicle_deed_koro2_exodrive_airspeeder.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.vehicle_system.vehicle_deed			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_armored_bantha	Pet Deed: Armored Bantha Mount	Normally docile and easily domesticated, banthas are perfect travelling companions.  This armored bantha will be happy to give you a ride on any planet in the Galaxy and is armored in the event that you are assaulted by criminals along the way.  This item may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/mount_deed_armored_bantha.iff							4		item.special.nomove,npc.pet_deed.reward_pet_deed			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_swamp_speeder	Vehicle Deed: Swamp Speeder	Developed by Aratech during the Clone Wars, the swamp speeder uses a hybrid repulsorlift/vectored fan propulsion system that allows it to hover aloft without touching the tough terrains of the planets where it is assigned.  Formerly an infantry support platform, this vehicle has been modified for civilian use around the Galaxy.  This item may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/vehicle_deed_swamp_speeder.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.vehicle_system.vehicle_deed			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_creature_pet_deed_massiff	Massiff Feeding Bowl	The feeding bowl of a burly carnivore found on both Tatooine and Geonosis.  Massiffs have coarse skin, large jaws, toothy mouths, big dark eyes, and a line of hard spines along their backs.  Generally domesticated by Tusken Raiders as camp guards, or by Geonosian for ridding their hives of vermin, this massiff has been domesticated just for you!  Release him inside your house so that you always have a friend waiting for you when you return home.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/creature_pet_deed_mastiff.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_pet_controller			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_empal_surecon_center_medical_table	EmPal SuRecon Center Medical Table	A surgical table from the most prestigious medical facility in the Galaxy, the Emperor Palpatine Surgical Reconstruction Center.  Medical tables like this one have saved, reconstructed, and improved the bodies of many important individuals throughout the Galaxy.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/decorative_empal_surecon_center_medical_table.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_wampa_skin_rug	Wampa-Skin Rug	A fine rug made out of the most fearsome creature to ever roam the icy plains of Hoth.  Warm and cozy, a rug of this quality immediately shows visitors in your home that you are an individual of refined taste and class.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/decorative_wampa_skin_rug.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_target_dummy	Target Dummy Controller	Combat lovers, take notice, AB-US3 is the latest innovation in galactic training.  Whether you choose to blast him from a distance, or assault him with a lightsaber, AB-US3 can take whatever you've got to throw at him.  A handy damage log keeps track of exactly what attacks you use on him and how much damage you do.  You can even invite your friends over to abuse him too.  Best of all, he doesn't complain... much.  This item may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/target_dummy_deed.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.target_creature_deed			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_house_sign	House Sign	Tired of your regular old house sign?  Is your business not getting the attention it deserves?  Give your structure an upgrade and let people know that you are a person of style and sophistication!  This brand new illuminated sign will help your building stand out and get the attention of anybody who happens to be passing by.  This item may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/item/skillmod/skillmod_tcg_set3_hanging_standing_sign.iff									item.special.nomove,systems.sign.special_sign			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_mandalorian_skull_banner	Mandalorian Skull Banner	This traditional Mandalorian crest, frequently mistaken for a Bantha skull, was actually adopted in reverence to a legendary Mandalorian combat-training master, Jaing.  Master Jaing's face resembled the symbol.  This item is #3 in a series of four Build-A-Jetpack items.  Combine this item with Build-A-Jetpack items 1, 2, and 4 to create a Merr-Sonn JT-12 jetpack.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/combine_object_mandalorian_skull_banner.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_combine_tcg_items			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_merr_sonn_jt12_jetpack_blueprints	Merr-Sonn JT-12 Jetpack Blueprints	Blueprints from Merr-Sonn Munitions, Inc detailing the parts and assembly of their Merr-Sonn JT-12 jetpack.  This compact jetpack features a warhead in its center column and was a favorite jetpack of the late bounty hunter Jango Fett.  This item is #4 in a series of four Build-A-Jetpack items.  Combine this item with Build-A-Jetpack items 1, 2, and 3 to create a Merr-Sonn JT-12 jetpack.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/combine_object_merr_sonn_jt12_jetpack_blueprints.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_combine_tcg_items			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_mustafar_travel_advertisement	Mustafar Travel Advertisement	Come visit Mustafar, one of the hottest vacation destinations in the Galaxy!  Ride a lava flea on an exciting volcanic tour or float down the lava river on a heat shielded repulsorlift platform.  Either way, a vacation to Mustafar is one you and your family will never forget!	object/tangible/tcg/series3/decorative_mustafar_travel_advertisement.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_hoth_travel_advertisement	Hoth Travel Advertisement	Come take a trip to the fabulous frozen plains of Hoth.  Explore the beautiful ice caves, enjoy and exhilirating ride on a tauntaun, or hit the slopes for the best skiing in the Galaxy.  For those with an adventurous streak you can test your skills as you go big game hunting for the elusive and deadly wampa.  Whatever thrills you seek, Hoth is the one destination that delivers for the entire family!	object/tangible/tcg/series3/decorative_hoth_travel_advertisement.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_swg_tcg_painting	Star Wars Galaxies Trading Card Game Painting	An image depicting of the battle between the Sith Namman Cha and Jedi Rachi Sitra during the campaign to reconstruct the Codex of Tython.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/decorative_swg_tcg_painting.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_darth_vader_obi_wan_diorama	Darth Vader vs. Obi-Wan Kenobi Diorama	A scene depicting the fateful moment when Darth Vader encountered Jedi Obi-Wan Kenobi aboard the Death Star.  Though Lord Vader won this legendary battle, it is said that Kenobi left no body behind after being defeated.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/decorative_darth_vader_obi_wan_diorama.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_guise_of_the_master	Guise of the Master	Harness the power of the Force and display it for all to see.  This item will make your eyes glow green.  This item may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/wearable_guise_of_the_master.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_gargans_hands_of_seduction	Gargan's Hands of Seduction	This is a powerful dancing enhancement known only to those of Askajian descent.  It was named after Yarna D'al Gargan, daughter of an Askajian chieftan.  When used, a mesmerizing glow will eminate from the hands of the user.  This item may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/reuseable_buff_gargans_hands_of_seduction.iff							4		item.special.nomove,item.buff_worn_item			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_greeter_battle_droid	Employment Terminal: Battle Droid Greeter	Employment Terminal: Tired of having to greet visitors to your home yourself?  Then you need this recently refurbished Trade Federation battle droid to greet anyone who enters your home.  This droid may sound a bit disgruntled by his new station in life but, rest assured, he is guaranteed not to attack you or start a planetary invasion.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/greeter_deed_battle_droid.iff						1	4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_greeter_contract			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_greeter_toydarian	Employment Terminal: Toydarian Greeter	Employment Terminal: No Jedi will dare try any mind tricks on you after they're greeted by this Toydarian as they enter your home.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/greeter_deed_toydarian.iff						1	4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_greeter_contract			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_greeter_tusken	Employment Terminal: Tusken Raider Greeter	Employment Terminal: Ferocious and ready for battle, this Tusken Raider is ready to intimidate (greet) anyone who dares to enter your home.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/greeter_deed_tusken.iff						1	4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_greeter_contract			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_nightsister_vendor	Employment Contract: Nightsister Vendor	Employment Contract: Straight from the bogs of Dathomir, this Nightsister is excited about the prospect of becoming your vendor and helping you sell things from the comfort of your own house.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/vendor_deed_nightsister.iff						1	4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_vendor_contract			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series3_battle_droid_vendor	Employment Contract: Battle Droid Vendor	Employment Contract: Show your support for the former Trade Federation by using this retired battle droid as a vendor in your house.	object/tangible/tcg/series3/vendor_deed_battle_droid.iff						1	4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_vendor_contract			
item_tcg_merr_sonn_jt12_jetpack_deed	Vehicle Deed: Merr-Sonn JT-12 Jetpack	A deed for the Merr-Sonn Munitions, Inc. JT-12 personal jetpack. This older model jetpack was first manufactured prior to the Clone Wars. 	object/tangible/tcg/series3/deed_tcg_merr_sonn_jt12_jetpack.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.vehicle_system.vehicle_deed			
item_special_sign_halloween_hanging_sign	Crescent Moon House Sign (Hanging, Version II)	Tired of that old house sign that everyone in the neighborhood has? Switch it out for this Galactic Moon Festival inspired sign instead! ||This updated sign version will allow you to consume and use the Galactice Moon Festival sign as a part of the new structure sign system.	object/tangible/item/skillmod/skillmod_halloween_event_hanging_sign.iff									item.special.nomove,systems.sign.special_sign			halloween item version 2
