item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_child_bed_02_01	Child's Bed	This bed features sheets displaying the heroes and villains of the Galactic Civil War.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/decorative_child_bed_01.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_medical_table_02_01	Polis Massan Medical Table	This medical table was taken from medical laboratories of the asteroid colony Polis Massa.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/decorative_medical_table_01.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_chewbacca_statuette_02_01	Chewbacca Statuette	A meter-tall statue of a figure well known in both the underworld and the Rebel Alliance.  Chewbacca is a wise and sophisticated warrior from the planet Kashyyyk.  Since escaping Imperial slavery Chewbacca has been co-pilot of the Millennium Falcon, Han Solo's elusive smuggling ship.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/decorative_chewbacca_statuette.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_han_solo_statuette_02_01	Han Solo Statuette	A meter-tall statue of the famous smuggler-turned-hero of the Rebel Alliance.  Han Solo is charming, impulsive, and he's blessed with a lucky streak that balances his arrogance.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/decorative_han_solo_statuette.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_stuffed_tauntaun_02_01	Tauntaun Stuffed Animal	Let's be honest, tauntauns smell really bad.  This toy has all the adorable qualities of a tauntaun but we've left out all the wretch-inducing aroma.  You're welcome.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/decorative_stuffed_tauntaun.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_stuffed_tauntaun			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_stuffed_wampa_02_01	Wampa Stuffed Animal	All the soft and cuddly aspects of having a wampa without the need to worry about having your feet frozen in a block of ice while you wait patiently for a large beast to come eviscerate and devour you.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/decorative_stuffed_wampa.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_stuffed_wampa			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_leia_and_r2_diorama_02_01	Princess Leia & R2-D2 Diorama	Pursued and outgunned by an Imperial Star Destroyer, Princess Leia's Tantive IV falls into Darth Vader's hands.  Knowing that she only has moments before she is captured, Princess Leia gives the brave astromech R2-D2 the stolen plans to the dreaded Death Star.  This is a small scene depicting that key moment between these two heroes.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/decorative_leia_r2_diorama.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_tatooine_travel_advertisement_02_01	Tatooine Travel Advertisement	Tatooine's twin suns are calling you to this spectacular vacation getaway!  Experience first-hand the non-stop action of a moisture farm or the sultry night life of the Mos Eisley cantina.  Bring the entire family to meet the native Tusken Raiders and enjoy their curious rituals and customs.  The sands are beckoning you so book your vacation now!	object/tangible/tcg/series4/decorative_tatooine_travel_advertisement.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_kashyyyk_travel_advertisement_02_01	Kashyyyk Travel Advertisement	Enjoy the lush arboreal scenery from the treetop cities of Kashyyyk.  Vacationers can climb the wroshyr trees or sample a delicious gorryl slug.  And for the truly daring one romantic stroll with a Wookiee on the beaches of Kachirho and you'll know that there's no better vacation destination in the Galaxy.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/decorative_kashyyyk_travel_advertisement.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_droid_oil_bath_02_01	Oil Bath	Oil baths are quite useful for removing dust, dirt, and other debris that can  clog a droid's joints.  A well oiled droid is a happy droid.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/decorative_droid_oil_bath.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_generic_rug_02_01	Mysterious Rug	This rug bears a mysterious symbol seen on Boba Fett's armor.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/decorative_tcg_rug_01.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_geonosian_speeder_02_01	Vehicle Deed: Geonosian Speeder	This speeder, also known as a flitknot speeder, was a model of speeder bike built by the Huppla Pasa Tisc Shipwrights Collective and is similar to one used by the Separatist mastermind Count Dooku during the Clone Wars.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/vehicle_deed_geonosian_speeder.iff							2		item.special.nomove,systems.vehicle_system.vehicle_deed			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_senate_pod_02_01	Vehicle Deed: Senate Pod	Formerly a pod used in the Galactic Senate of the Republic, before the dissolution of the Senate by Emperor Palpatine, this pod has been repurposed for multi-passenger atmospheric travel.  This item may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/vehicle_deed_senate_pod.iff							2		item.special.nomove,systems.vehicle_system.vehicle_deed			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_tauntaun_ride_02_01	Antique Tauntaun Ride	Bring back the good ol' days of the Old Republic with this vintage tauntaun ride.  Nostalgia will overflow in your guests when they see this breathtaking collectible right in your home.  This ride is in pristine condition, still works, and plays the original musical track it was released with.  Be careful though; you'd better not sit on it or you may break it.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/decorative_tauntaun_ride.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_tauntaun_ride			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_video_game_table_02_01	M'a Jong's Galactic Tiles Arcade Cabinet	The second in the hit series of M'a Jong Galactic Tiles games sweeping the galaxy, this new design features an ergonomic cabinet with seating and bold new game graphics.  This fun and engaging matching game may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/video_game_table.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_video_game_series4			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_balta_podracer_02_01	Balta-Trabaat BT310 Podracer	More commonly referred to as a Quadra-Podracer due to its four turbine engine design, this Balta-Trabaat BT310 Podracer is similar to the one flown by Ben Quadinaros in the Boonta Eve Classic.  While speedy, this quad-engine design can be temperamental.  This item may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/vehicle_deed_balta_podracer.iff							2		item.special.nomove,systems.vehicle_system.vehicle_deed			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_peko_peko_mount_02_01	Toxic Peko-Peko Mount	This nightmarish creature was raised and mutated by the notorious Dr. Evazan.\A0 The maniacal doctor subjected this peko-peko to countless acts of experimentation and cruelty even prior to it being hatched.\A0 Dr. Evazan hoped to create an invincible creature that would serve as a protector that would also be a capable of a quick getaway.\A0 This item may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/mount_deed_peko_peko.iff							2		item.special.nomove,npc.pet_deed.reward_pet_deed			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_falleens_fist_02_01	Falleen's Fist Blueprints	These are the blueprints to the personal skyhook of Black Sun leader, Prince Xizor.  When activated this item provides a 50% increase on all resources gathered when hand sampling or space mining for one hour.  This item is consumable.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/consumable_falleens_fist.iff						1	4		item.special.nomove,item.buff_click_item,object.autostack			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_ball_of_peace_02_01	Ball of Peace	The Ball of Peace was a symbol of unity and freedom given to the Gungan people by the citizens of Theed after the Trade Federation invasion of Naboo.  This item, when activated, grants the user a free profession respec.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/consumable_ball_of_peace.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.respec.click_combat_token,object.autostack			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_t16_toy_02_01	T-16 Skyhopper Toy	"A small replica of Incom's T-16 Skyhopper for every young ""hot rodder"" child.  This toy provides an instant experience gain of 20% of the total amount needed to reach the next level. Characters at level 90 will instead receive a random collection item. This item is consumable."	object/tangible/tcg/series4/consumable_t16_toy.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_instant_xp_grant,object.autostack			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_relaxation_pool_deed_02_01	Structure Deed: Muunilinst Relaxation Pool	The Muunilinst Relaxation Pool represents a new concept of luxury and sophistication in an age often marked by war and violence.  Come soak in the tranquil pools as you stare upward at the sky though a raised sunroof.  This structure consumes four lots and may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/structure_deed_relaxation_pool.iff							4		item.special.nomove,item.structure_deed.player_structure_deed			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_creature_pet_deed_nuna_02_01	Nuna Feeding Bowl	Fond of galactic vermin?  This little guy is for you!  Nuna are flightless fowl native to the swamps of Naboo (i.e., they're swamp turkeys).  While they may be ungainly and unattractive, they are also quite cute in a strange way and can make excellent pets.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/creature_pet_deed_nuna.iff							4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_pet_controller			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_guise_of_vapaad_02_01	Guise of Vaapad	Named after lightsaber form VII, developed by Jedi Master Mace Windu, this item will make your eyes glow as purple as Mace Windu's lightsaber blade.  This item may only be claimed once per character.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/wearable_guise_of_vapaad.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_chandrilan_dress_02_01	Chandrilan Dress	A dress similar to the one worn by Mon Mothma during the last days of the Old Republic.  This dress is an ideal outfit for debating Imperial law or for a special night on the town!	object/tangible/tcg/series4/wearable_chandrilan_dress.iff							4		item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_location_itv_02_01	ITV: Corellian G9 Rigger Freighter	"This Corellian G9 Rigger freighter is an instant transport vehicle that can be programmed to take you to any three locations of your choosing, regardless of the planet that you may be on.  As one of the very first ships of its class to be outfitted with a hyperdrive, this bucket of bolts may be old, but it's definitely useful!  A similar ship is said to have been used for ""unofficial errands"" by Anakin Skywalker during the Clone Wars.  This item may only be claimed once per character."	object/tangible/tcg/series4/instant_travel_terminal_location.iff							3		systems.veteran_reward.instant_travel_terminal_deed			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_home_itv_02_01	ITV: Geonosian Solar Sailer	This instant transport vehicle will take you directly to your home, regardless of the planet that you may be on.  Solar sailers are luxurious starships that travel upon solar winds by means of a large solar sail.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/instant_travel_terminal_home.iff							3		systems.veteran_reward.instant_travel_terminal_deed			
item_tcg_nuna_rotten_egg_02_01	a batch of rotten eggs	From the looks of the mess, it seems your Nuna has laid a batch of bad eggs.  Taking these eggs outdoors and placing them in the wild seems the best thing to do.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/house_pet_rotten_egg.iff							1		systems.tcg.tcg_pet_extras,item.special.nomove			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_vendor_kitonak_02_01	Employment Contract: Kitonak Vendor	Employment Contract: A Kitonak vendor for use in your house.  Native to Kirdo III, Kitonak's have the ability to seal vulnerable body openings in folds of flesh to protect them from harsh environments.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/vendor_deed_kitonak.iff						1	4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_vendor_contract			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_vendor_toydarian_02_01	Employment Contract: Toydarian Vendor	Employment Contract: Toydarians are shrewed bargainers who like to socialize and strike deals.  Thus, this Toydarian is the perfect vendor for your house.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/vendor_deed_toydarian.iff						1	4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_vendor_contract			
item_tcg_loot_reward_series4_greeter_palowick	Employment Terminal: Pa'lowick Greeter	Employment Terminal: A greeting just sounds better when uttered from bright red lips at the end of a flexible trunk.  Visitors to your home or business will be absolutely enchanted with your Pa'lowick greeter.	object/tangible/tcg/series4/greeter_deed_pa_lowick.iff						1	4		item.special.nomove,systems.tcg.tcg_greeter_contract			
